## 2. Phase 1 — Launch Critical Fixes
**Goal:** Resolve launch blockers and interface bugs.

---

### Task 1.1: Fix Monospace Font Fallbacks & UI Integration
- **Why This Matters:** High-end pricing and property specifications must look clean and professional. Because `--font-mono` is missing in the CSS theme, the browser falls back to the default monospace font, which looks outdated.
- **Expected Impact:** Immediate alignment of price tags, specification tables, and metadata chips with the Montserrat/JetBrains editorial system.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Very Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 2 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Define `--font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;` in `@theme inline` inside [styles.css](file:///c:/Users/Ky/cc/src/styles.css).
  - Verify that the JetBrains Mono Google Font family imports successfully.
  - Verify that property card specs and price labels render in JetBrains Mono.
- **Priority:** P0

---

### Task 1.2: Persistent Saved Bookmarks (Local Storage Sync)
- **Why This Matters:** High-ticket real estate purchases require multiple return visits. Wiping the user's bookmarks list on page refresh breaks trust.
- **Expected Impact:** Users can build and return to their property shortlists across multiple browser sessions.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 3 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Modify `savedList` state in [properties.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Ky/cc/src/routes/properties.tsx) to check `localStorage` for `cityqlo_saved_properties` on mount.
  - Sync updates to `localStorage` when properties are added or removed.
  - Confirm saved items persist after browser refresh.
- **Priority:** P0

---

### Task 1.3: Scroll-to-Results on Collection Selection
- **Why This Matters:** When users click a lifestyle collection card, the grid updates below the fold. Without scroll feedback, users assume the website is broken.
- **Expected Impact:** Connects the user's click with search results and reduces bounce rates.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 2 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Update `handleSelectCategory` to trigger `scrollToResidences()` when category changes.
  - Verify smooth transition alignment across mobile and desktop viewports.
- **Priority:** P0

