## 4. Phase 3 — Trust & Credibility System
**Goal:** Establish transparency and confidence.

---

### Task 3.1: Developer Reputation Badging & Tooltips
- **Why This Matters:** Luxury buyers invest in developer credibility. Raw text labels fail to communicate quality.
- **Expected Impact:** Reassures buyers regarding delivery quality and construction standards.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 6 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Add an interactive badge next to developer names on property cards.
  - Hovering/clicking the badge opens a tooltip displaying credentials (e.g., "Triple-A Builder", "100% Delivery Rate").
- **Priority:** P1

---

### Task 3.2: Precise Construction Timelines & Turnover Progress
- **Why This Matters:** Buyers need clear visibility into completion quarters to coordinate cash flows.
- **Expected Impact:** Reduces buyer hesitation when evaluating pre-selling properties.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 6 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Display the specific turnover target (e.g. "Est. Completion: Q4 2028") next to pre-selling badges.
  - Add a progress bar indicating construction milestones for pre-selling listings.
- **Priority:** P1

---

### Task 3.3: Verified Listing Badges
- **Why This Matters:** Real estate listings are often plagued by duplicate or outdated data.
- **Expected Impact:** Confirms database authenticity and encourages buyers to submit inquiries.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Easy
- **Estimated Time:** 4 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - Display a verified checkmark badge (`[✓ VERIFIED]`) on all validated property listings.
  - Add a brief tooltip explaining the listing verification check.
- **Priority:** P1

---

### Task 3.4: Advisory Profiles & Agent Assignment
- **Why This Matters:** High-ticket real estate requires personal relationships. Anonymous listings fail to build trust.
- **Expected Impact:** Humanizes the platform and increases contact rate by linking properties to expert advisors.
- **Technical Difficulty:** Medium
- **Estimated Time:** 16 Hours
- **Dependencies:** None
- **Acceptance Criteria:**
