## 8. Phase 7 — Analytics & Growth Infrastructure
**Goal:** Track user actions to optimize conversion paths.

---

### 8.1 Core Tracking Events

| Event Name | Trigger | Properties | Business Use |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `property_viewed` | Listing detail page loads. | `property_id`, `property_slug`, `developer`, `category`, `price_min` | Measures interest distribution across different properties. |
| `property_saved` | User clicks the bookmark heart. | `property_id`, `property_name`, `source_action` (e.g. "card_heart", "details") | Identifies high-demand properties. |
| `inquiry_initiated` | User opens the inquiry modal. | `property_id`, `property_name`, `entry_point` (e.g. "card_inquire", "sticky_mobile") | Pinpoints friction points if forms are opened but not submitted. |
| `inquiry_submitted` | User submits the inquiry form. | `property_id`, `property_name`, `has_phone`, `investment_timeline` | Core conversion event for cost-per-lead calculation. |
| `filter_used` | User changes search settings. | `filter_type` (e.g., "price", "location"), `filter_value` | Informs inventory acquisitions based on buyer search criteria. |
| `collection_selected` | User clicks a collection card. | `collection_id`, `collection_title` | Monitors interest in Metro Core, Suburban, and Resort tiers. |
| `guide_download_submitted`| User submits form to download guide. | `user_name`, `investment_timeline`, `email` | Tracks guide download lead conversions. |

