## 9. Phase 8 — Technical Debt & Architecture
**Goal:** Clean up the codebase for speed, scalability, and accessibility.

---

### 9.1 Core Issues & Technical Debt Risks

| Issue | Risk | Recommended Fix | Est. Effort |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :---: |
| **No Monospace CSS theme token configuration.** | Fallbacks render in system fonts. | Map `--font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;` in `styles.css`. | 1 Hr |
| **State-only bookmarks data storage.** | Shortlists wipe on page reload. | Sync the bookmark array to `localStorage`. | 3 Hrs |
| **Hardcoded colors in TSX markup.** | Fragmented design elements. | Replace all hardcoded colors with `var(--color-primary)` references. | 6 Hrs |
| **Missing screen reader tags.** | Inaccessible to assistive tech. | Add `aria-label` tags to image sliders, bookmark hearts, and icons. | 4 Hrs |
| **Inline layout calculations.** | Slower performance during rendering. | Use CSS styles and tailwind variables for image aspect ratios. | 8 Hrs |

