## 13. Launch Readiness Criteria

Before deploying the updated platform to production, the release must meet the following criteria:

- [ ] **Performance:** Main thread loads in <1.5 seconds on standard mobile connections.
- [ ] **Accessibility:** All focus states are visible; contrast ratios pass WCAG AA standards.
- [ ] **Database Integrity:** Lead forms route safely to Supabase backend targets.
- [ ] **Data Persistence:** User bookmarks persist across test sessions.
- [ ] **Visual Consistency:** No raw hex color declarations remain in property elements.
